Privacy Policy for Astro Math
Last updated: October 10, 2024
This Privacy Policy explains how Astro Math (referred to as "we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, discloses, and protects your personal information when you use our mobile application or other related services (collectively, the "Service"). By using the Service, you agree to the collection and use of your data in accordance with this Privacy Policy.
