2. How We Use Your Information
We may use the personal data we collect for various purposes, such as:
To provide, operate, and maintain the Service
To manage your account and respond to your requests
To send you updates, notifications, or marketing communications (if opted in)
To analyze Service usage and improve performance
To comply with legal obligations
3. Sharing Your Information
We may share your personal data under the following circumstances:
With Service Providers: We may share your data with third-party companies that help us operate the Service, such as hosting, analytics, or support providers.
For Legal Reasons: We may disclose your data to comply with legal obligations or protect our rights and property.
4. Data Retention
We will retain your personal data only for as long as necessary for the purposes stated in this Privacy Policy. Usage data may be retained for a shorter period unless required for security or legal purposes.
5. Data Transfers
Your information may be transferred to and maintained on servers located outside your state, province, or country where data protection laws may differ. By submitting your information, you consent to such transfers.
6. Data Deletion
You have the right to request the deletion of your personal data. You can do this by contacting us or through your account settings (if applicable). Please note, we may retain certain data for legal or security purposes.
7. Security of Your Information
We take reasonable measures to protect your personal data, but please note that no method of transmission over the Internet or method of electronic storage is completely secure.
8. Children's Privacy
Our Service is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children under 13. If you become aware that a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us.
9. Links to Other Sites
Our Service may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these websites.
10. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last Updated" date.
